         <abstract>
            <p>A basis for the space of $C^1$ piecewise polynomials in two variables of degree $n \geqslant 5$ is constructed. The basis is parametrized by "nodal variables," namely, the values and derivatives of the basis functions at a discrete set of points.</p>
          </abstract>
